- ✅ `AsSpan`-based concatenation used correctly in `FixedLengthTruncator` left branch (L65-67)
- ✅ `AsSpan`-based concatenation used consistently in `FixedNumberOfCharactersTruncator` (L134, L148)
- ✅ No `.Substring()`, `.ToLower()`, or missing `StringComparison` issues
